    "Open the \"Shortcuts\" application, and choose one of the Roam shortcuts. Then add a [keyboard shortcut](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) to it" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"افتح تطبيق \"الاختصارات\"، واختر واحداً من اختصارات روم. ثم أضف إليه [اختصار لوحة المفاتيح](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32)\""
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Öffnen Sie die Anwendung \"Shortcuts\" und wählen Sie eine der Roam-Verknüpfungen aus. Fügen Sie dann eine [Tastenkombination] (https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) hinzu."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Abre la aplicación \"Atajos\" y elige uno de los atajos de Roam. Luego añade un [atajo de teclado](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) a este."
          }
        },
        "es-419" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Abra la aplicación \"Atajos\" y elija uno de los atajos de Roam. Luego agregue un [atajo de teclado](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) a este."
          }
        },
        "fil" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Buksan ang aplikasyong \"Shortcuts\", at pumili ng isa sa mga shortcut ng Roam. Pagkatapos ay magdagdag ng [keyboard shortcut](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) dito."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ouvrez l'application \"Raccourcis\" et choisissez l'un des raccourcis Roam. Ensuite, ajoutez un [raccourci clavier](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) à celui-ci."
          }
        },
        "fr-CA" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ouvrez l'application \"Raccourcis\" et choisissez l'un des raccourcis Roam. Ensuite, ajoutez-y un [raccourci clavier](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32)."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Open the \"Shortcuts\" application, and choose one of the Roam shortcuts. Then add a keyboard shortcut to it."
          }
        },
        "pa" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"ਸ਼ੌਰਟਕੱਟਜ਼\" ਐਪਲੀਕੇਸ਼ਨ ਖੋਲੋ, ਅਤੇ ਰੋਮ ਸ਼ੌਰਟਕੱਟਜ਼ ਵਿਚੋਂ ਇਕ ਚੁਣੋ। ਫਿਰ ਇਸ ਨੂੰ [ਕੀਬੋਰਡ ਸ਼ੌਰਟਕੱਟ](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) ਜੋੜੋ।"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Abra o aplicativo \"Atalhos\" e escolha um dos atalhos do Roam. Em seguida, adicione um [atalho de teclado](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) a ele."
          }
        },
        "pt-PT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Abra a aplicação \"Atalhos\" e escolha um dos atalhos Roam. Em seguida, adicione um [atalho de teclado](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) a ele."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Mở ứng dụng \"Shortcuts\", và chọn một trong số các lối tắt Roam. Sau đó thêm một [phím tắt](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32) vào đó."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "打开\"快捷方式\"应用程序，并选择Roam的一个快捷方式。然后，为其添加一个[键盘快捷方式](https://support.apple.com/guide/shortcuts-mac/launch-a-shortcut-from-another-app-apd163eb9f95/7.0/mac/14.0#apd94a0e7c32)。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
